{"tid":824826,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"教育局宣布明日所有學校繼續停課","createTime":"2018-09-17T08:51:14.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-24T08:33:12.000Z","uid":164435,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"0fcedfdaecb8fc9670fc0ba21a3d6bb519919a69","tid":824826,"uid":164435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T08:51:14.000Z","msg":"由於強颱風山竹對學校造成不同程度影響，部分學校需時清理及維修校舍和設施，加上公共交通服務尚待完全恢復正常，為確保學生的安全，教育局宣布明日（九月十八日）所有學校停課。<br />\n<br />\n　　在安全的情況下，學校應保持校舍開放，並實施校本應急計劃，安排人手在校內安全的地方照顧有確切需要回校的學生。家長應考慮家居環境、附近的道路交通情況、學生的照顧等因素決定是否送子女回校。<br />\n<br />\n  <br />\n <br />\n完<br />\n2018年9月17日（星期一）<br />\n香港時間16時45分<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/201809/17/P2018091701226.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.info.gov.hk%2Fgia%2Fgeneral%2F201809%2F17%2FP2018091701226.htm&d=zY%2FQSSMQZOo%2Fp9VqewScKpUWI6eGpREPWAa3TRi9Bo4%3D&h=6a04c1fc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/201809/17/P2018091701226.htm</a>"},{"pid":"094383ddcca491c02c9f90b35f58a0ec5cd2307a","tid":824826,"uid":164435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T08:53:14.000Z","msg":"唔知大學跟唔跟呢"},{"pid":"054337f10a5bbdca5ff7e8e4746311f1b7b3e348","tid":824826,"uid":49974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T16:21:13.000Z","msg":"Ok收到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13b0dee8fe3e749f373f47f69a2da05174b399a8","tid":824826,"uid":49974,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-19T07:27:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6690b9c621697a1cfb863e523b1437513ebcab7f","tid":824826,"uid":49974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-19T07:28:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" clas